OL,3,C'No one is listening to us': Fear and
OL,4,Cfrustration as migration tensions grow
OL,6,FFrom the north west coast of our
OL,7,Fkingdom to the western fringes of the
OL,8,Fcapital, our journey over the past few
OL,9,Fweeks has revealed just how deep the
OL,10,Ffissures are in this divided kingdom.
OL,12,FIn Blackpool, we saw how migration can
OL,13,Fpitch some of the poorest people in
OL,14,Fthe land against those with even less.
OL,16,FIn Wolverhampton, racially motivated
OL,17,Fviolence is again instilling fear in
OL,18,Fthe local community.
