OL,6,FStanwell is a thriving, ethnically
OL,7,Fdiverse community. No one accepts that
OL,8,Fthe protests have a racial element.
OL,10,F--> 'It's an excuse to be racist': How
OL,11,Ftensions over asylum hotels are
OL,12,Fdividing Blackpool
OL,14,F"I have loads of friends of different
OL,15,Fraces," the girl explained. "If this
OL,16,Fwere racist, I wouldn't be standing
OL,17,Fhere right now."
OL,19,FThere is certainly no mistaking the
OL,20,Foverwhelming emotion - frustration.
