OL,6,F"No one is listening to us," we were
OL,7,Ftold repeatedly.
OL,9,FAnd no one expects a solution to the
OL,10,Funderlying causes.
OL,12,FLast year saw a record number of
OL,13,Fpeople claiming asylum in the UK
OL,14,F(108,000 according to the Migration
OL,15,FObservatory at Oxford University),
OL,16,Fwhile by August, the numbers crossing
OL,17,Fthe channel in small boats had topped
OL,18,F50,000 since the Labour government
OL,19,Fcame to power.
