OL,8,FIn the midst of a cost-of-living
OL,9,Fcrisis and amid high levels of legal
OL,10,Fimmigration, there is tension that can
OL,11,Fbe easily exploited.
OL,13,F"I'm more worried now than I have ever
OL,14,Fbeen about extremism," Nigel Bromage,
OL,15,Ffrom Exit Hate, who works to reclaim
OL,16,Fyoung people who've fallen prey to the
OL,17,Ffar right, said.
