OL,6,FThe protests make propaganda for the
OL,7,Factivists who lurk online, he said,
OL,8,Fwhere young people in particular spend
OL,9,Fso much time.
OL,11,F"I often say if somebody knocked on
OL,12,Fyour door and he had a swastika arm-
OL,13,Fband on, and you had a son and
OL,14,Fdaughter upstairs, you'd never let
OL,15,Fthem in to talk to them.
OL,17,F"But because many parents don't know
OL,18,Fwhat their children are looking at
OL,19,Fonline, that's exactly what's
OL,20,Fhappening."
